&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Are you a former nurse, enrolled nurse or midwife with the desire and drive to return to practice?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen within Mid Yorkshire Hospital NHS Trust for previously registered nurses and midwives wishing to return to practice and deliver high quality compassionate and care. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are currently recruiting positions to complete a return to practice programme in partnership with Bradford University. Our mentors will support you to achieve your learning outcomes within your clinical area.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Course date 8th February 2021&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For further information on return to practice please contact:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Charlene Pressley,07857664667 or email charlene.pressley@nhs.net.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
